*Frances Lannon, ''The Spanish Civil War, 1936–1939'' (Oxford: [[Osprey Publishing|Osprey]], 2002)
*Frances Lannon, ''Lady Margaret Hall, Oxford: the First 125 Years, 1879–2004'' (Oxford: Lady Margaret Hall, 2004)

